practitioner.alt: Dr. Mutaz Alqawasmeh, Specialist Orthopedic Surgeon, Book appointment online, Book Specialist Orthopedic Surgeon online, Motor City, Dubai, UAE, Okadoc - Book doctor appointment online
practitioner.about:
Dr. Mutaz Alqawasmeh qualified as an orthopaedic specialist from the Omar Almukhtar University in Albyda, Libya. He has rich work experience gained during his association with the Alalam Medical Centre in Saudi Arabia and the Jordanian Ministry of Health.

He is a member of medical associations related to his specialisation, such as the Jordanian Orthopaedics Board, the Jordan Medical Council, the AO Trauma Foundation and the Jordan Osteoporosis Prevention Society.

Dr. Alqawasmeh works in the areas of orthopaedics and sports medicine. He treats osteoarthritis, and performs specialised surgical procedures such as arthroscopic surgery of the knee and shoulder and joint replacement of knee and hip joints.

When Dr. Mutaz Alqawasmeh gets some time off work, he pursues his passion for reading and football. He speaks Arabic and English.
